      "updated": 0,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "AI that predicts WHERE you'll fail BEFORE it happens,\nand tells you HOW to fix it.\n\nNobody owns the space between:\n\"Your code has a bug\" (pre-prod AI)\n\"Your service is down\" (observability)\n\"Run a chaos experiment\" (infrastructure layer)",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 11
    },

