      "seed": 72,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 72,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 0,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "⚠ CodRabitt / Qodo could expand into production resilience\n   → They focus on CODE layer, not production. Different swim lane.\n\n⚠ Microsoft / Google could enter\n   → Enterprise sales cycles are 12-18 months. You ship in weeks.\n\n✓ Your speed advantage: ship fast, iterate, niche down\n✓ Target: startups + SMBs with k8s who can't afford full SRE teams",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10
    },

